{
  "texts": [
    "Facebook is one of the most popular social media platforms across many regions and has an estimated 3.06 billion monthly active users.",
    "1 The platform enables users to share digital content, advertise products, and establish community connections, making it a suitable area for our investigation.",
    "Personalized recommendations are given on most social media platforms, including Facebook.",
    "Still, explanations justifying these recommendations are not readily available and easily accessible to users (Bilgic & Mooney, 2005; Haque et al., 2023; Laato et al., 2022; Zhang & Chen, 2020).",
    "Moreover, in recent years, the significance and need for explainable recommendations have also increased due to the introduction of various privacy policies and guidelines like GDPR 2 and recommendations from expert groups such as the EU's High-level Expert Group on AI (AI HLEG)."
  ]
}